        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5264a3e5-378c-4adc-984c-e94180609849).Image",
        "Description": "Princess Diana has been taken captive by the King of Evil and it&apos;s up to you to rescue her, 47!\r\rBut wait! Before you can face the King, you&apos;ll need to take care of his three loyal minions, who are keeping Diana prisoner. Cleanse these demons with a blast of holy light!\r\rOnce the Princess is safe, you must infiltrate the castle and confront the King. Remember that only the might of the Holy Sword will be enough to defeat him for good.\r\rOh great hero, have courage and go forth!",
